# Test 2: Variables and arithmetic
Set x to 10.
Set y to 5.
Set sum to x plus y.
Set diff to x minus y.
Set prod to x times y.
Set quot to x divided by y.

Show "x = " plus x.
Show "y = " plus y.
Show "x + y = " plus sum.
Show "x - y = " plus diff.
Show "x * y = " plus prod.
Show "x / y = " plus quot.

# Test power operation
Set power to 2 raised to 8.
Show "2^8 = " plus power.
